          "title": "The Ivim as distinct from the Pelishtim, originating from Teiman",
          "display_title": "Ivim from Teiman",
          "timestamp": "05:59"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Apparent trivialities in the Torah revealing profound significance",
      "display_title": "Torah's Hidden Meaning",
